verbose_text: Avoca ASU, a combination of ASU and glucosamine sulfate, has been shown to suppress TNF-alpha, IL-1beta, COX2, iNOS, PGE2, NF-kappaB activation and nitrite production in articular chondrocytes and monocytes / macrophages, reducing pain and inflammation in OA patients.
